Net::Address::IPv4::Local 0.10
A class for discovering the local system's IP address.
(C) 2005 Julian Mehnle <julian@mehnle.net>
<http://www.mehnle.net/software/net-address-ipv4-local>
===============================================================================

Net::Address::IPv4::Local discovers the local system's IP address that would be
used as the source address when contacting "the internet" or a certain
specified remote IP address.

